               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝsār for the first half of the year (fols. 3ra-145vb): 
 I-1)
                     Maskaram (fols. 3ra-27vb)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 28ra-48va)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār
                     (fols. 49ra-71rc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols. 72ra-98vc) 
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols.
                     99ra-127vc)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols. 127ra-145vb) 
 The commemorative
                     notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
