                  <provenance>The donor of the Ms. was probably Gabra
                     Māryām (Gabru), mentioned, in the supplications formulas fols 3ra, 3va, 5rb,
                     5va (added by a secondary hand), and also esp. in Additio 1. Other names are
                     also mentioned: Walatta Mǝhrat (s. e.g. <locus target="#4vb">4vb</locus>, 4vc,
                     5vc, 6vb), Walatta Yoḥannǝs (s. e.g. <locus target="#11ra">11ra</locus>, 20rb,
                     23rc, 24rb), Gabra ʾAbǝya ʾƎgziʾ (s. e.g. <locus target="#12ra">12ra</locus>,
                     12va, 17vb, 19vc), Walda Hǝywat (s. <locus target="#46vb">46vb</locus>), Gabra
                     ʾIyasus (s. <locus target="#46vb">46vb</locus>).
 The spaces for the
                     rubricated donor´s name in the supplications has not been filled after <locus target="#79r">79r</locus>.</provenance>
               </history>
